---

<Layout
  title="Why Source Commodities Direct from Africa Instead of Through Middlemen | Origin Direct Group"
  description="The real cost of middlemen in African commodity trade. Data on markup chains, traceability benefits, and why direct sourcing saves 20-550% depending on the commodity."
  structuredData={[articleSchema, breadcrumbSchema]}
>
  <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
